value:
You can hear all sorts of stories while
guarding a gate. I ended up privy to a
lot of what was happening in Fódlan.

It was my job to make sure no one
suspicious got inside Garreg Mach.
No villain will ever get past me!

Getting called to Askr was a real
shock, but I've got great instincts
when it comes to stuff like this.$k$pAlthough, I never could've imagined
what it actually feels like to be
summoned to another world!

Today...there is quite a bit to report!
I saw a girl transform into a dragon!
...What? That happens all the time?!

Sharena asked if I was the gatekeeper
everyone's been talking about lately...
But why would they talk about me?

Nothing to report from
$Nf's castle!

You can count on me to protect the
gates with everything I've got!

Let's battle with all our might and
pray we win this thing, so that we
both can survive!

I will pour my heart and soul into
improving so that I can become
an even better gatekeeper.

For me? Really?! ...In that case, I'll
use this strength to make sure the
gates are secure, no matter what!

Greetings! What a pleasu—wait, this
isn't the monastery! ...Askr? Uh huh...
Well, thanks for having me!

Greetings, $Nu!$k$pThanks for all your hard work!
There's nothing to report today!$k$pUm... That said, can I talk to you
about something?$k$pTo be honest, I couldn't understand
why a lowly gatekeeper like me was
summoned to Askr.$k$pI mean, there are so many incredible
Heroes! You've got warriors, nobles,
and even gods from all these worlds...$k$pBut you know what I realized? I don't
need to be any of those things to help.
Just being me is more than enough!$k$pSo I'm going to focus on what I CAN
do. Even if they bring an entire army,
I won't let a single enemy get inside!$k$pUntil the day comes when everyone
in Askr can live peaceful, joyful lives,
I will protect the gates.

Greetings, summoner! Nothing to report!
Thought you could sneak up on me? Hah! Not a chance!
Being in a new world just means I have to stay more vigilant than ever!
I'm under strict orders to keep my eyes up and stay on guard.
Huh. There's no fishing pond around here. Where are people supposed to catch fish?
No matter where I'm stationed, my only concern is protecting the gate.
Nothing to worry about, summoner! Not even a suspicious bug could crawl past me!
